WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.651
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.651 --> 00:00:03.192
How y'all been doing?

00:00:03.584 --> 00:00:08.712
I'm going to go over a word that I gave 10 months ago.

00:00:10.344 --> 00:00:21.746
It was on one of the big prophecy channels, and they were talking about it, questioning whether it was really a real visit or a vision from the Lord.

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:38.104
Rightfully so, there's a lot of flaky stuff on YouTube, but I'm going to tell you this: it's genuine, it's real, and the Spirit of the Lord spoke to me just like He does many times.

00:00:40.116 --> 00:01:00.799
I honestly don't even watch these channels that talk about this stuff because I'm very sensitive to the Spirit of God, and there are a lot of false prophets out there.

00:01:00.799 --> 00:01:12.320
Whenever I hear it, immediately I know if that is not the Lord or if it is the Lord.

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:24.835
If I get a mixed bag on that channel, I don't go back to it.

00:01:24.835 --> 00:01:28.379
I'm just saying.

00:01:28.379 --> 00:01:37.399
People ask who it is, but that's between you and God.

00:01:37.399 --> 00:01:52.766
I'm not going to tell you who I believe is a false prophet on YouTube; that's just not what we're going to do.

00:01:55.731 --> 00:02:21.725
What I want to tell you is that after taking time to pray over this—it's been about 11 months since I gave this word—I asked the Lord what He showed me about the big asteroid.

00:02:22.460 --> 00:02:41.954
I believe that Tom Horn gave that word before he went home to be with the Lord about Apophis, which I believe is Wormwood.

00:02:46.095 --> 00:02:55.164
It talks about it in the Book of Revelation, that there will be a massive asteroid that hits the Earth.

00:02:55.422 --> 00:03:13.226
I believe that what the Lord showed me was this massive asteroid that is scheduled to hit in 2029.

00:03:29.399 --> 00:03:36.605
It's supposed to hit the planet Earth and it's going to be huge; supposedly, NASA has even talked about it being ginormous.

00:03:36.605 --> 00:03:44.570
I want to go over again what the Lord showed me.

00:04:01.908 --> 00:04:02.314
I was standing outside praying, and I had an open-eyed vision.

00:04:02.314 --> 00:04:26.111
When this happened, it was so real that I could actually hear it at the same time I was seeing in the spirit this massive event.

00:04:37.479 --> 00:04:41.175
I was standing by a carport and all of a sudden, this massive asteroid came.

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:55.986
It was so fast and so loud it deafened your ears because the sonic boom was so powerful.

00:05:05.351 --> 00:05:05.582
It was the size of a major building, a humongous rock.

00:05:08.182 --> 00:05:21.462
It came out of the sky and shook everything, breaking the windows of all the houses.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:31.444
It was moving so fast you could barely see it—like a fireball with a humongous fire trail behind it.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:44.785
It was shaking your whole entire being as it came in from the West to the East.

00:05:44.785 --> 00:05:52.228
When it came in, it crashed out by San Juan, Puerto Rico.

00:05:52.228 --> 00:06:14.865
The United States government was trying to shoot this massive asteroid down, but because it was moving so quickly, they could not hit it with a rocket.

00:06:14.865 --> 00:06:21.039
They tried to hit it with a massive green laser beam.

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:31.560
In the spirit, I could see this beam come out of the Alabama-New Orleans area.

00:06:31.560 --> 00:06:50.297
I don't know if there's a massive laser beam like that down by the Gulf area, but the beam shot across America.

00:06:50.297 --> 00:07:04.467
Whenever it hit over the Tennessee-Kentucky area, they hit it with that laser.

00:07:08.743 --> 00:07:19.982
It cut it in half, but it didn't destroy it; it split into three pieces.

00:07:19.982 --> 00:07:47.013
Those pieces hit the Earth, and while I don't remember where they all hit, the major part of that rock hit by San Juan, Puerto Rico.

00:07:47.013 --> 00:07:59.480
The impact was so massive it sent a humongous tidal wave.

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:21.750
I tried to give an estimate last time, saying it was several hundred feet high, but it was much more than that.

00:08:22.420 --> 00:08:27.766
It covered all the islands, including the Bahamas.

00:08:33.573 --> 00:08:41.200
There was a massive tsunami wave that came up out of the ocean at the speed of sound.

00:08:41.404 --> 00:08:49.566
It was so fast that people did not have time to evacuate.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:08:58.862
I saw the water covering all the islands: St.

00:08:58.862 --> 00:09:00.173
Martin, St.

00:09:00.173 --> 00:09:07.229
Thomas, San Juan, Haiti, Cuba—all were completely saturated and wiped out.

00:09:07.229 --> 00:09:15.386
If you weren't high in the mountains, you were destroyed.

00:09:19.965 --> 00:09:28.925
The wave came into Florida, hitting Miami, Fort Lauderdale, and the whole Atlantic coast.

00:09:29.350 --> 00:09:40.554
This massive tsunami came miles inland, wiping out major hotels and houses on the Atlantic seaboard.

00:09:40.554 --> 00:09:48.960
It went all the way up to Cape Hatteras Island in North Carolina.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:59.989
Part of the tsunami went clear into Africa and Europe, wiping out places in England.

00:10:08.018 --> 00:10:13.445
It was moving so quickly that people didn't have time to evacuate and were caught up in the water.

00:10:17.147 --> 00:10:17.716
This was a very powerful experience.

00:10:19.470 --> 00:10:26.417
I believe this is Wormwood; I really believe this is Apophis.

00:10:29.178 --> 00:10:44.495
A lot of people say that it is supposed to miss the Earth in 2029, but I believe we're going to have a direct impact soon.

00:10:44.495 --> 00:10:59.600
Whether the Rapture of the church has taken place first or this is part of it, I don't know.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:10.160
I'm not a Bible scholar; I just pray and the Lord shows me things to warn people that Jesus is coming.

00:11:10.160 --> 00:11:15.839
These are the signs of the times.

00:11:15.839 --> 00:11:21.782
We are in the last of the last days.

00:11:21.782 --> 00:11:33.507
We are getting so close to the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:11:33.507 --> 00:11:43.777
This was an actual thing that the Lord showed me in prayer.

00:11:43.777 --> 00:12:00.839
If you hear the voice of the Lord telling you to move out of a certain area, you need to listen to Him.

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:15.289
We are going to experience things we've never thought we would see in the coming days.

00:12:15.289 --> 00:12:31.770
I believe Jesus is coming sooner than many think, but nobody knows the day or the hour.

00:12:34.700 --> 00:12:40.245
Have an expectation inside of you for His coming.

00:12:40.245 --> 00:12:53.222
Be excited and have a sense of urgency, like Noah was when he was building the ark.

00:12:53.222 --> 00:13:05.160
As in the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:12.580
Only eight people entered the ark then; people were not expecting the flood.

00:13:12.580 --> 00:13:19.068
Today, people are not expecting Jesus to come back.

00:13:19.068 --> 00:13:25.131
Their hearts have become hardened and they seek fleshly things.

00:13:25.131 --> 00:13:32.287
They have an appearance of godliness but deny the power thereof.

00:13:32.287 --> 00:13:35.552
Many have itching ears.

00:13:35.552 --> 00:13:47.713
Even in the body of Christ, the church hasn't preached the truth of holiness and repentance.

00:13:47.713 --> 00:13:59.279
They've fallen away into a seeker-friendly gospel—milky words with a little porridge.

00:14:02.738 --> 00:14:07.457
The body of Christ in those churches is anemic and starving spiritually.

00:14:07.457 --> 00:14:11.600
I'm telling you, Jesus is coming soon.

00:14:22.676 --> 00:14:22.944
I hope you're watching for Him and your heart is ready.

00:14:22.944 --> 00:14:38.729
We're going to see signs in the heavens, and this is a major sign prophesied in the Bible.

00:14:40.655 --> 00:14:51.608
Father, I thank You for every person watching, excited about the coming of Your Son.

00:14:51.608 --> 00:15:08.959
Thank You, Lord, that Jesus died for us and rose again so that we don't have to go to a devil's hell.

00:15:08.959 --> 00:15:14.789
We have an expectation of Your Son's soon return.

00:15:14.789 --> 00:15:22.360
We are looking for You daily, keeping our lamps full of oil.

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:47.891
I know there will be a lot of lives lost as the Book of Revelation tells us, but I thank You that You said You didn't want any to perish.

00:15:55.839 --> 00:15:56.014
I thank You that people are repenting and coming closer to You today.

00:15:56.014 --> 00:16:14.560
If we're here when Apophis hits, I thank You, Lord, that believers will hear Your voice and You will quicken their spirits to get out quickly.

00:16:19.480 --> 00:16:22.400
We give You all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:16:32.140 --> 00:16:32.465
In the mighty name of Jesus, amen.
